      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ENHANCE (1) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by 1.3 lengths at Murray Bridge Straight in a handy 19.73 beating Our Beaver. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Expected to be right there at the finish again. DOUBLE HELIX (2) is in top form scoring comfortably at last two, winning by 2.5 lengths (30.51) last time and by 7 lengths (30.24) two back. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Deserves serious consideration again. DASHING NANDO (7) has mixed form but was in the money three back and wasn't far away last time at Angle Park when fourth (30.94) in a Grade 6. Well placed here and should do much better. CLAYMORE LASS (8) good strike-rate and a bold showing is expected here.",
